Helps with google maps, see googles online[http://code.google.com/apis/maps/documentation/reference.html] reference.

== Short way:

Generate a sample map and look at the code...
  script/generate map 


==Long way:

=== In your layout
  include_google_javascript :key => GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY

=== In your view or layout
  google_map :fullscreen => true

=== In your View Helper or View
  def init_map
    run_map_script do
      map = Google::Map.new(:controls => [:small_map, :map_type],
                            :center => {:latitude => -33.947, :longitude => 18.462},
                            :zoom => 12)
    end
  end